flowchart TB
    TASK["研究任务输入"] --> RP["Research Planner（任务拆解）"]

    RP --> DA["Data Analyst"]
    RP --> MA["Macro Analyst"]
    RP --> FA["Fundamental Analyst"]

    DA --> CA["Causal Analyst（因果链构建）"]
    MA --> CA
    FA --> CA

    CA --> SA["Scenario Analyst（三情景推演）"]
    SA --> PA["Portfolio Analyst（组合影响评估）"]
    PA --> WA["Wealth Advisor Agent（客户适配方案）"]

    WA --> HUMAN{"人工确认节点"}
    HUMAN -->|确认通过| CR["Compliance Reviewer（合规审核）"]
    HUMAN -->|退回修改| WA

    CR --> EA["Evidence Auditor（证据审计）"]
    EA --> RI["Report Integrator（报告整合输出）"]

    CR -.不合规回退.-> RP
    EA -.证据不足回退.-> DA
    EA -.因果链存疑回退.-> CA